rawplus_visdt

rawplus_visdt.Rd

Visits (visdt) data in rawplus format.

Usage

rawplus_visdt

Format

a data frame with 28093 rows and 48 columns.

studyid

string Study Identifier

siteid

string Site Identifier

invid

string Investigator ID

scrnid

string Screen Identifier

subjid

string Subject Identifier

subjectid

string System Subject Identifier

datapagename

string eCRF Page Name

datapageid

string Internal ID for Data Page

foldername

string Folder Name

instancename

string Instance Name

recordid

string Record Identifier

record_dt

string Record Date

recordposition

float Record Position

mincreated_dts

string Earliest Data Creation Date/Time

maxupdated_dts

string Latest Data Update Date/Time

visit_dt

string Visit Date

peperf

string Complete Physical Exam Performed

pereasnd

string Reason Physical Exam Not Performed

svvs

string Vital Signs

svaecm

string Evaluation of AE and/or CM

svecg

string ECG

svpk

string PK and Associated Dose

svlab

string Lab Evaluations

svpregtest

string Pregnancy Test

svsd

string Study Drug Adjustment or Dispensation

svothsp

string Other Specify

subjid_nsv

string SUBJECT IDENTIFIER

scrnid_nsv

string SCREENING IDENTIFIER

subjinit_nsv

string SUBJECT INITIALS

invid_nsv

string INVESTIGATOR ID

subject_nsv

string Subject name or identifier

instanceid_nsv

double Internal id for the instance

folder_nsv

string Folder OID

folderseq_nsv

double Folder sequence number

visitdat_nsv

timestamp Visit Date

visitdat_yy_nsv

double Visit Date_Year

visitdat_mm_nsv

double Visit Date_Month

visitdat_dd_nsv

double Visit Date_Day

peperf_std_nsv

string Complete physical examination performed? Coded Value

svvs_nsv

double Vital Signs

svaecm_nsv

double Concomitant Medications

svecg_nsv

double ECG

svpk_nsv

double PK and Associated Dose

svlab_nsv

double Lab Evaluations

svpregtest_nsv

double Urine Pregnancy Test

svsd_nsv

double Study Drug Adjustment or Dispensation

svhcc_nsv

double HCC Surveillance

svhcc_raw_nsv

string HCC Surveillance_(Character)
